# mini.jsonl — tiny SYNTHETIC labeled dataset for the eval harness.
# One JSON object per line: { "query": "...", "relevant": ["id", ...] }.
# `relevant` lists the corpus ids (see mini-corpus.jsonl) that SHOULD be retrieved for the query.
# Lines beginning with # and blank lines are ignored.
