{"query":"Where do code projects live on disk?","relevant":["m03"]}
{"query":"What is the agent-cockpit?","relevant":["m02"]}
{"query":"How does the reranker relate to fusion and decay?","relevant":["m08","m09"]}
{"query":"benchmarks for scoring long-term memory recall","relevant":["m06"]}
